divs: Sighting DetailsIt was early in the morning around 7-8,i was just getting outside for my first smoke,when i looked up as i always do when its dark.Then i saw this triangular grey,almost visible with 3 red light in the corners.It was almost right above my hed,in same heigts as the trees.It just fly by,and i was a bit shaky because it wasnt espected to see this just after getting out of bed.It wasnt the first time a saw some strange object in my life.
